<div class="panel-region-separator"></div><div class="panel-pane pane-views-panes pane-widgets-latest-cltv galt-child galt-child-latest_cltv" >
  
    <div class="block-title-wrapper">
    <h3 class="pane-title">Latest from CLTV</h3>
    <div class="line"></div>
    </div>
  
  
  <div class="pane-content">
    <div class="view view-widgets view-id-widgets view-display-id-latest_cltv view-dom-id-60dd5c5c5d8d102964613f8e66e5ab3e">
    
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
      


  <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first">
    <article class="node card node-type-media node-display-card" data-nid="158278">
    <a href="/cltv/2020/04/media-treats-trump-kid-gloves-liberate" title="Media Treats Trump With Kid Gloves On &#039;Liberate&#039; Tweets">
      <img src="https://videocafe.crooksandliars.com/files/imagecache/node_teaser/mediaposters/2020/04/44837.jpg" alt="Media Treats Trump With Kid Gloves On &#039;Liberate&#039; Tweets" class="card-img-top" />
</a>

    <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-title">
            <h4><a href="/cltv/2020/04/media-treats-trump-kid-gloves-liberate"  title="Media Treats Trump With Kid Gloves On &#039;Liberate&#039; Tweets">Media Treats Trump With Kid Gloves On 'Liberate' Tweets</a></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-text">
                        The media asked Trump gentle questions about his tweets inciting insurrection in three states, and meekly accepted his answers.        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="card-footer">
        <div class="pull-right">
            Apr 18, 2020        </div>
        <span class="node-submitted">By <a href="/user/aliza-worthington" title="View Aliza Worthington&#039;s profile and posts">Aliza Worthington</a></span>
    </div>
</article>
  </div>

  
  <div class="views-row views-row-2 views-row-even">
    <article class="node card node-type-media node-display-card" data-nid="158275">
    <a href="/cltv/2020/04/stephen-moore-compares-coronavirus" title="Stephen Moore Compares Coronavirus Protesters To Rosa Parks">
      <img src="https://videocafe.crooksandliars.com/files/imagecache/node_teaser/mediaposters/2020/04/44836.jpg" alt="Stephen Moore Compares Coronavirus Protesters To Rosa Parks" class="card-img-top" />
</a>

    <div class="card-body">
        <div class="card-title">
            <h4><a href="/cltv/2020/04/stephen-moore-compares-coronavirus"  title="Stephen Moore Compares Coronavirus Protesters To Rosa Parks">Stephen Moore Compares Coronavirus Protesters To Rosa Parks</a></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="card-text">
                        In an appearance on the Freedom on Tap Youtube show, Moore discussed helping protesters in Wisconsin, and urged more such “civil disobedience.”        </div>

    </div>
    <div class="card-footer">
        <div class="pull-right">
            Apr 18, 2020        </div>
        <span class="node-submitted">By <a href="/user/scarce" title="View Ed Scarce&#039;s profile and posts">Ed Scarce</a></span>
    </div>
